1. Download the source tarball

   $ wget http://osp.googlecode.com/files/OSP-1.0.tar.gz


2. Extract the contents

   $ tar xvzf OSP-1.0.tar.gz


2. Run the setup script

   $ cd osp
   $ ./scripts/setup.sh


For far more detailed installation documentation, including an
explanation of each step in the setup script, visit
http://code.google.com/p/osp/wiki/Installation.
